<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Настройка чекаута</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12">
    <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800">Настройка чекаута</h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800">10 шаг</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500"> из 11</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-1.5 mb-4">
            <div class="bg-purple-600 h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 90%;"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Вы в любой момент сможете поменять стиль позже</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">Содержание</h2>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="fast_order" class="mr-2"><label for="fast_order" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Быстрый заказ</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="order_content" class="mr-2"><label for="order_content" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Состав заказа</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="desired_time" class="mr-2"><label for="desired_time" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Желаемое время</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="address" class="mr-2"><label for="address" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Адрес</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="pickup" class="mr-2"><label for="pickup" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Подъезд</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="floor" class="mr-2"><label for="floor" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Этаж</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="intercom" class="mr-2"><label for="intercom" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Домофон</label></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">Оплата</h2>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="cash" class="mr-2" checked><label for="cash" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Наличные</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="online" class="mr-2"><label for="online" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Онлайн на сайте</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="card_courier" class="mr-2"><label for="card_courier" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Картой курьеру</label></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 mb-4">Тип доставки</h2>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="self_pickup" class="mr-2"><label for="self_pickup" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Самовывоз</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="delivery" class="mr-2"><label for="delivery" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Доставка</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="planned_delivery" class="mr-2"><label for="planned_delivery" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Плановая доставка</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="delivery_cost" class="mr-2"><label for="delivery_cost" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Стоимость доставки</label></div>
                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="free_delivery" class="mr-2"><label for="free_delivery" class="text-sm text-gray-600">Бесплатная доставка от</label></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6">
            <button class="text-sm bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded">Назад</button>
            <button class="text-sm bg-purple-500 hover:bg-purple-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded">Дальше</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="flex items-center justify-between mt-12 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <div>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-800">Политика конфиденциальности</a>
            <span class="mx-2">•</span>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-800">Способы оплаты и возврата</a>
            <span class="mx-2">•</span>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-800">Условия обработки персональных данных</a>
        </div>
        <div>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-800">Контакты</a>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
